longBusinessSummary: Manufacturing Integration Technology Ltd, an investment holding company, designs, develops, manufactures, and distributes automated equipment for semiconductor and other industries in China, Singapore, Europe, the United States, and Asia. The company operates through Built-To-Print and Customised Automation segments. It also offers contract equipment manufacturing services; manufactures and repairs lifting and handling equipment; and components for electronic and semiconductor industries. The company was incorporated in 1992 and is headquartered in Singapore. Manufacturing Integration Technology Ltd is a subsidiary of MIT Technologies Pte Ltd.
